    "UIName": "Freya MBT",
    "Id": "vehicledef_Freya",
    "Name": "Frey MBT",
    "Details": "Created by Quicscell to capitalise on the 3rd succession war, the Freya was a massive success. Sales wildly exceeded expectations and within a few years, the Freya was being fielded by every great house and a number of periphery nations. A 75 ton tank, Quickscell opted for speed and armor protection over raw firepower; and as such the Freya boasts a fairly anaemic weapons loadout for its weight. An AC/10 backed up by a pair of Machine Guns and a pair of SRM-4s makes up the weapons load, while a 300 rated fusion engine allows the tank to hit speeds of 60kph.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 4/6 hexes / 120/180 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       240     40\n<b>Left</b>         190     40\n<b>Right</b>       190     40\n<b>Rear</b>        150     40\n<b>Turret</b>      190     40\n\n<b>Total</b>      960    200</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Main Battle Tank</color>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_freyamainbattletank"
  },
